{
  "stem": "9601.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The rest of us in the village, all that them now, even Chaika, her sister, knew how to speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was the only one that did not speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I used to go and visit there, I could not understand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How is it possible?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here's a Jewish little girl who speaks no Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, eh-- it's like comment to an American.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You say look at it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All these little kids speak English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Terrific.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You forget something there, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my Grandma Kobylanski and her little granddaughter-- must have been four-- three or four years old-- they stayed together over there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think people-- from what I understand, people looked after them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So when the destruction of the Jews was issued, and they came to gather them up, they went to my Grandma Tesler's house, and the Korn's house, Korn-Adler.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they gathered them all up, and they took them out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, you saw the picture of the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took them all over there, and they murdered them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The people that did the murder, the shooting, the killing of them, were not natives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were people from another village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This way, you can accuse the natives of doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You do the dirty work in my village, and I'll do your dirty work in your village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Who's going to know the difference?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Strangers came and did it, not us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Tricky, isn't it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Very-- very thought-- figured out how to do, how to carry out this charge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And who did it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The college students, the gymnasiums, the intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "How do I know that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "When we were traveling from Stakh's place to Zumer's place, we got caught in daylight.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
